title: Selected by DNSK - Acoustic Mixtape 1.0
description:
Presenting a mixtape with a fine selection of acoustic pieces. All tracks are hand picked as well as remastered by me. This mixtape was created on a sunday, and suits just for that - a relaxed afternoon in the end of the week. 

Enjoy this release that hopefully will create peace and mindfulness within you.



01. Duffy - Mercy
02. Suzanne Vega - Luka
03. Taken by Trees - Sweet Child O' Mine
04. Acoustic Hits - Hotel California
05. Art Of Dying - Sorry
06. James Vincent McMorrow - Wicked Game
07. Janet Devlin - Friday I'm In Love
08. Crosby & Nash - Lay Me Down
09. Matt Johnson - Your Song
10. Maria Doyle Kennedy - How You Remind Me
11. Cat Power - (I Can't Get No) Satisfaction
12. Damien Dempsey - Sunday Bloody Sunday
13. Michael Collins - Fast Car
14. John Mayer - Slow Dancing in a Burning Room
15. Extreme - More Than Words
